title: Asiwome Ameko
text:
Thanks for stopping by my little corner. My name is Asiwome Ameko, and I’m excited to meet you.
Health Data Analyst at the Trust Research Data labs, working on areas including health data analytics, clinical data management, health econometrics and spatial data science.
Also working as a Health Information Officer at the Tamale teaching Hospital, where I doing a lot of health data management, analytics and reporting tasks, support clinical staffs and researchers from research study design to publication of results.



University of Cape Coast | Cape Coast, Ghana
Msc Data Management and Analysis | In-progress
University of Health and Allied Sciences | HO, Ghana
Bachelor of Public Health (Health Information) | 2012 - 2017



Health Information Officer (2021-Present) | Tamale teaching Hospital
Health Data Analyst (Independent Consultant) (2019-Present) | Trust Research Data labs
